        {
            "text": "One day my sister and I were walking near the road.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9635.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "A big truck was driving down the hill.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9636.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "A car was speeding up the hill.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9637.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "The truck driver was talking on his mobile phone. He was not looking at the road.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9641.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "The truck smashed into the car!",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9639.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "An ambulance and the police came to help.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9640.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Two tow trucks came. One towed the truck. The other towed the car.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9638.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We saw everything. We were shocked.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/9642.png"
        },
